This is a mailing to the employees of ETH Zurich


Ladies and gentlemen

Once again, you can benefit from the Neptun promotional sale. In
collaboration with Apple, HP and Lenovo we offer laptop computers -
including a 3 year warranty - at very attractive prices.

The web shops and information about the demo-days can be found on our
website at:
http://www.projektneptun.ch/index_EN.ntml

Essential facts:

- All laptops are cutting-edge and use the current Intel Core i5 and i7
processors ("Sandy Bridge").
- All laptops are available with Swiss or US keyboard.
- Our offers are valid for private as well as official orders. Please
make sure your order is in compliance with the guidelines of your
institution if you are placing an official order.

* Apple:
- As in the past, we offer the Apple laptop models currently available
in the AppleStore.

- The four recommended Neptun Apple configurations include a full 3-year
AppleCare Protection Plan (APP).

- The Neptun discount is valid for all MacBook Pro and MacBook Air
laptop configurations! Please note: Individually configured Apple
laptops do NOT automatically include the warranty extension (APP)! We
recommend adding it to the shopping cart in order to protect your
investment.

For details:
http://www.projektneptun.ch/index.php/apple-laptop-offers_EN.html

* PC:
- The product range comprises four laptop models per manufacturer from
their respective top business lines (HP: EliteBook, Lenovo: ThinkPad)
plus one netbook. The prices are highly attractive - to some extent due
to the low USD.

- The laptops come with a three year warranty which may be extended up
to five years.

- Again, the HP and Lenovo laptops can also be acquired without
operating system - at a discount, of course. Please note that you must
have a valid licence if you plan on using a commercial operating system.

For details: http://www.projektneptun.ch/index.php/pc-laptop-offers_EN.html

* Displays:
For the first time, we are also offering displays. NEC is the winner of
our recent evaluation. We offer four sizes: 22", 23", 24" and 27".

- Displays of 23" or larger use IPS technology giving you better color
and the stability of the viewing angle is much wider compared to common
TN panels.

- Ergonomics: full height adjustability, swivel, tilt and pivot
functionality.

- In addition, we offer the new Apple Thunderbolt Display at a discount.
If you buy an Apple Display in addition to a MacBook, the laptop APP is
automatically extended to the display.

For details: http://www.projektneptun.ch/index.php/displays_EN.html


* We have partnered up with Logitech for some special peripheral offers
and we have also extended the product range:
http://www.projektneptun.ch


- For anyone interested in Linux we recommend:
http://www.projektneptun.ch/index.php/events_EN.html

- You can offset carbon emissions associated with a laptop's life cycle
in the myclimate carbon offset project:
https://www1.ethz.ch/neptun/services/myclimate/index_EN


Don't hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or suggestions.

Kind regards,
Lisa von Boehmer
Dominik Candreia
